Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight\Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body\Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{=45}will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy hurries for Navy HQ in order\Nto stop his brother, Ace, from being executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, at Navy HQ on Marineford,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's greatest pirate, Whitebeard, has finally shown himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He cracked the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A seaquake! He's distorting the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still wanna run wild,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,run as wild as you want on the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you people call him Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he calls us "sons."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all hated by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So it makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's just a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it still makes us happy.
