Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me not to go but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who told you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who told him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that we put you through so much, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody in this world knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to someone who messes with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...our crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let anybody\Nwho hurts you get away with it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Count on us! We will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves, Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought this upon ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On this side, we, the Warlords,\Nthe Navy's greatest powers—3 admirals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and a hundred thousand elite soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On that side, there are the Whitebeard Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and more than 40 allied ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do you wanna do it, Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna be on the sideline as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you just came to kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There are rowdy men everywhere and I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He is also a man but he is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm praying for you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is receding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is flying backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really smooth just two minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why all of the sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! My waterworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Finally it stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We went back a good distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when we can get to Marineford like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.08,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Wh-What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hurry up? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta get there before Ace's execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Luffy-kun. We'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll-y roll-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think your Fishman Karate can help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you gonna call out whale sharks to help again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My power is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who are you depending on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He said we'll make it! So we'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"He said we'll make it! So we'll make it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stick around here any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your dream\Nto become the King, Captain Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If the time is right,\NI'm sure that there'll be a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's too early,\Nthen I'll just wait for the right timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're gonna just give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, can't you see his magnificent confidence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It doesn't look like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what they call "perfect composure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the regal presence to become the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that miracles don't happen that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is nothing I can do but wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The tide has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just steering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could this be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle that you were talking about is about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's happening but this is it! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see it, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is calling me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying "come and become the King!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so great! Like no other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! It seems like we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They've quieted down all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they waiting for Whitebeard's command?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The water level is rising again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the ground rumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The seaquake that he set up before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming in the form of a tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tremor-Tremor Fruit made him a quake man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Edward Newgate a.k.a. Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a giant tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that our superior forces\Nwill guarantee us victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We could well fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that man has...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...the power to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beginning! The war!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The invaders: a fleet of 47 ships\Nfrom the New World led by Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The defenders: the 2 greatest forces\Nof the Government—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy HQ and the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who wins and who loses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the times will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tsunami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He certainly is the legendary monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Age!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Pheasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You young squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Admiral Kuzan did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Partisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole bay is frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The ships can't move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We have the greatest force\Nof Navy HQ—the admirals—on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to be afraid of the Whitebeards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Destroy the Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a good foothold now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them what we're capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The commanders came out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount a counter-offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be the 5th division commander—\NFlower Sword Vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay alert, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all mighty soldiers—\Nnot just the commanders! Don't forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I got it, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to have ice in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my blood is burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's shoot them up and invade the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here come the vice admirals of Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so rare to see all of them together at the same place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like when they have the Buster Call. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...when it comes to Pops\Nand us, it won't work that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuru-san, why don't you stand back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it up to us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and have some tea or something from a comfortable distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk smart to me, fledglings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no safe place\Neven if I back up to the end of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the ship to the ice gorge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Trounce them all and get to the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be happy to give our lives for Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not scared of Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Squard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Warlord on the move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very unusual!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The capricious Hawk-Eye seems like he's willing to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to figure out the true distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...between us and that man\Nwho seems like right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They say even the most skilled fighters\Nare struck by fear, left unable to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just by looking into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hawk-Eye" truly suits him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's every swordsman's dream to cross swords with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he is assumed to be the strongest in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the instinct of swordsmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Black Blade\Nthat everybody's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's the Black Blade "Night!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the only\NTwelve Supreme Grade Swords in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And its dark blade edge has an irregular temper line and a double clove pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a noted sword suitable for the greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihawk and Yellow Monkey launch their attacks on Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In response, the Whitebeard commanders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,fight back using their own powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As the unpredictable battle rages,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Admiral Red Hound finally unleashes his incredible power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"An All-Consuming Inferno!! Admiral Red Hound's Power!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
